name: OggConvert
description: OggConvert is a small practical media conversion tool with multiple media file formats. It can directly drag and drop media files to convert and set the audio/video converting quality.

en_US.description: OggConvert is a small practical media conversion tool with multiple media file formats. It can directly drag and drop media files to convert and set the audio/video converting quality.
en_US.name: OggConvert

zh_CN.description: OggConvert是一款小巧实用的媒体转换工具，它可以支持直接拖拽媒体文件进行转换，同时设定音频/视频转换的品质。还支持转换多种媒体文件格式。
zh_CN.name: OggConvert
